        "label": "Code Implementation — Hospital System",
        "description": "تنفيذ الكود لكل الشرائح الأربعة — كل شريحة تُبنى بشكل مستقل",
        "points": [
          "Tech Stack: Next.js 14 (App Router) + PostgreSQL + Prisma ORM",
          "Architecture: Monorepo — shared types + per-slice modules",
          "Auth: Role-based (doctor, nurse, receptionist, technician, pharmacist, admin)",
          "Budget: ~2000 سطر backend + ~3000 سطر frontend لكل الشرائح"
        ]
      },
